results.deck: Crystal Dynamics is a California based developer founded in 1992. Once an independent developer and publisher, they are now currently apart of Square Enix.
results.description:
Overview

Crystal Dynamics are perhaps best known for the Legacy of Kain franchise and the latest entries in the Tomb Raider franchise.
